<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="applaud-v">applaud <strong><em>v</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'plɔːd/    美 /ə'plɔːd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>鼓掌；称赞；赞成：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>People stayed silent and listened to us, and applauded at the end.
人们静静地听我们说，最后为我们鼓掌。</p><footer>译林⑦ – 3</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I applaud your decision.
我赞成你的决定。</p></div></div>